text:
My grand daughter just graduated fr this kindergarten
The graduation event was arranged very well, well planned, parents can see the accomplishment in detail.  Principal Tina did a good job as well as Teachers Yu Hang and Dianna . They are caring, helpful and warm.
Highly recommend this school.

One of the most beautiful churches I have ever visited.
Beautiful mass.
Beautiful priest, everyone so friendly for being a large Cathedral.
Worth a visit.
Church of the Good Shepard or the Catholic Cathedral of Singapore is an impressive church/cathedral. Well run and kept. With a wind pipe organ being played at every mass.
Newly renovated church compound. Parking is free, the showers are relatively nice and they host numerous events and collaboration with the boys n girls brigade
Great ambience. Went for the Saturday service at 4pm. Was a cosy setting, the people were friendly and had a relatively young crowd.
